OL,3,CTeacher unions to ballot members on
OL,4,Ctaking industrial action over pay
OL,6,FThree of the largest trade unions
OL,7,Frepresenting teachers in Northern
OL,8,FIreland have announced they will
OL,9,Fballot members on taking industrial
OL,10,Faction over pay.
OL,12,FThe National Association of
OL,13,FSchoolmasters Union of Women Teachers
OL,14,F(NASUWT), Irish National Teachers'
OL,15,FOrganisation (Into) and Ulster
OL,16,FTeachers' Union (UTU) said management
OL,17,Fhas failed to make a satisfactory pay
OL,18,Foffer for 2024/5.
