OL,3,CTeacher unions to ballot members on
OL,4,Ctaking industrial action over pay
OL,6,FThey said they have given notice to
OL,7,FEducation Minister Paul Givan that
OL,8,Fthey intend to ballot for industrial
OL,9,Faction.
OL,11,FA fourth union, the National Education
OL,12,FUnion (NEU), has announced an
OL,13,Findicative ballot of members in
OL,14,Frelation to the dispute.
OL,16,FIn a joint statement, the unions said
OL,17,Fthey are "making it clear to the
OL,18,Fminister that, if he wishes to avoid
OL,19,Findustrial action, he needs to make a
OL,20,Fsatisfactory offer on pay".
