OL,6,FThey also said they are committed to
OL,7,Fworking together to ensure that
OL,8,Fexisting workload agreements are fully
OL,9,Fimplemented at school level and that
OL,10,Fwork which has commenced in relation
OL,11,Fto the workload reviews continues to
OL,12,Fbe progressed with a sense of urgency.
OL,14,FNASUWT national official Justin
OL,15,FMcCamphill said teachers are being hit
OL,16,Fhard by increases in prices for food
OL,17,Fand energy.
