OL,6,F"When this is combined with high
OL,7,Finterest rates and ever increasing
OL,8,Frents, teachers cannot make ends
OL,9,Fmeet," he said.
OL,11,F"Teachers in Northern Ireland have
OL,12,Fwatched since the summer as their
OL,13,Fcounterparts in the rest of the UK
OL,14,Fhave received significant pay
OL,15,Fincreases for this academic year and
OL,16,Fare telling us that they are fed up
OL,17,Fwith being left behind.
