OL,3,CTeacher unions to ballot members on
OL,4,Ctaking industrial action over pay
OL,6,F"This situation has forced teachers
OL,7,Finto a position where they are left
OL,8,Fwith no choice but to put the minister
OL,9,Fon notice that they will take
OL,10,Findustrial action if a significant pay
OL,11,Foffer is not made forthwith."
OL,13,FMark McTaggart, from Into, said
OL,14,Fteachers are the "least well-paid
OL,15,Facross these islands".
