OL,3,CTeacher unions to ballot members on
OL,4,Ctaking industrial action over pay
OL,6,F"It would appear that the minister is
OL,7,Fcontent to allow the education system
OL,8,Fto sleepwalk into a crisis of
OL,9,Frecruitment and retention of teachers,
OL,10,Fand to allow talented teachers to be
OL,11,Ftrained for export," he said.
OL,13,F"Teachers across the north are once
OL,14,Fagain the least well-paid across these
OL,15,Fislands.
OL,17,F"Teachers have a right to receive a
OL,18,Fsalary that truly reflects their value
OL,19,Fto society.
