OL,3,CTeacher unions to ballot members on
OL,4,Ctaking industrial action over pay
OL,6,F"The continued failure by those who
OL,7,Fhold the purse strings to provide this
OL,8,Fhas the potential to have a
OL,9,Fdevastating effect on the life chances
OL,10,Fof the children and young people in
OL,11,Ftheir care."
OL,13,FJacquie White, from the UTU, urged Mr
OL,14,FGivan to address the issue as a matter
OL,15,Fof priority.
OL,17,F"It is disheartening, to say the
OL,18,Fleast, for our teaching workforce to
OL,19,Ffind themselves once again as the
OL,20,Flowest paid members of the profession
OL,21,Facross these islands," she said.
