OL,6,FPauline Buchanan, from the NEU, said:
OL,7,F"Since teachers last received a pay
OL,8,Frise in 2020/21, we have been living
OL,9,Fthrough a horrendous cost-of-living
OL,10,Fcrisis ` whilst prices have soared, no
OL,11,Fincrease has been made.
OL,13,F"The profession is undervalued and
OL,14,Funder-resourced, and this is leading
OL,15,Fto many making the difficult choice to
OL,16,Feither leave or teach elsewhere.
